com.mesosphere.sdk.scheduler.plan

Interface Element

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ParentElement<C>, Phase, Plan, Step
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractStep, DefaultPhase, DefaultPlan, DeploymentStep, DeregisterStep, EraseTaskStateStep, RecoveryStep, ResourceCleanupStep, TaskKillStep, TLSCleanupStep, TriggerDecommissionStep, UninstallStep

    public interface Element
    An Element is a generic component in a tree of elements. It is the basic unit for the description of Plans used to launch Mesos Tasks. Plans, @{link Phase}s and Steps are all implementations of Elements. Elements have Strategies (see: Strategy associated with them which describe when child elements should be presented as candidates for execution.
